@startuml
title Data types and MIP propagation flow
autonumber

participant "xforms:bind\n(model definition)" as BIND
participant "xforms-rebuild\n(L5296)" as REBUILD
participant "add-context mode\n(L5321)" as ADDCTX
participant "xforms-recalculate\n(L5392)" as RECALC
participant "recalculate-binding\n(L5431)" as RECALC_BIND
participant "xforms-revalidate\n(L5531)" as REVAL
participant "xsd-helpers.xsl\nxsdh:is-type-valid (L41)\nxsdh:canonical-type (L16)" as XSD
participant "DOM Controls" as DOM

== Rebuild Phase ==
BIND -> REBUILD : binds parsed from model
REBUILD -> ADDCTX : add-context mode\nresolve @nodeset to instance nodes
ADDCTX -> ADDCTX : annotate bind with\n@instance-context\n@nodeset (absolute)

== Recalculate Phase ==
RECALC -> RECALC_BIND : for each bind
RECALC_BIND -> RECALC_BIND : evaluate @calculate\n(try/catch for type coercion)
RECALC_BIND -> RECALC_BIND : evaluate @relevant\n(boolean coercion)
RECALC_BIND -> RECALC_BIND : evaluate @readonly\n(boolean, inherits from parent)
RECALC_BIND -> RECALC_BIND : evaluate @required\n(boolean)
RECALC_BIND -> RECALC_BIND : evaluate @constraint\n(boolean expression)

== Revalidate Phase ==
REVAL -> REVAL : check-required-fields (L1576)\nfor each required=true() binding
REVAL -> REVAL : check-constraints-on-fields (L1626)\nevaluate constraint expressions
REVAL -> REVAL : check-required-bindings (L1681)\nvalidate non-empty + required
REVAL -> REVAL : check-instance-xsi-types (L1706)\nvalidate xsi:type attributes
REVAL -> XSD : xsdh:canonical-type()\nnormalize type QNames
REVAL -> XSD : xsdh:is-type-valid()\nvalidate value against XSD type

== Refresh Phase (MIP Projection to DOM) ==
REVAL --> DOM : refreshOutputs-JS (L4345)\nupdate output values
REVAL --> DOM : refreshRelevantFields-JS (L4550)\nshow/hide based on relevant
REVAL --> DOM : getRelevantStatus (L4244)\ngetHtmlClass (L4175)\napply readonly/required CSS classes
REVAL --> DOM : dispatch xforms-valid\nor xforms-invalid events
@enduml
